{"tid":1979200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完世衛個Live，不得不承認陳奕迅唱歌真係好屈機","createTime":"2020-04-19T09:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T15:19:41.000Z","uid":353419,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4d4912ade476ba23dcf5b21ebaa535d0dc6f10","tid":1979200,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"近年都冇咩聽Eason的歌，但見佢第一次上國際舞台。<br />\n太好奇所以忍唔住入去睇下。<br />\n<br />\n全部歌手都係唱英文，得佢一個唱廣東話，感覺好特別。<br />\n對比之下，發覺陳奕迅唱歌好特別，雖則佢現今爛聲又走音，<br />\n但每一句都感染到人，令人陶醉。<br />\n<br />\n最難解釋的係明明佢啲歌唔難唱，亦冇用複雜的技巧，<br />\n但冇人唱到佢果種感染力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">利申：開Post係想同大家理性討論唱功，自己聽開純音樂，今次破例一次先聽Eason，唔該唔好屌我</span>"},{"pid":"7510ba53ef4f87513c3db883ae877fdc90f7fca8","tid":1979200,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"仲匿係屋企聽歌<br />\n你係咪香港人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8073c85c206e1a24e0acc5713eee9ccefef848","tid":1979200,"uid":239525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98b632a8f34c39689c079ec434743a0150ca6360","tid":1979200,"uid":11067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"WHO? whatever"},{"pid":"651704650820978d03f5949ffe11498004650e83","tid":1979200,"uid":307551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"又爛聲又走音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點解冇人講嘅"},{"pid":"d565c5d7eaef4ccbee0be829df08b4512869f4f7","tid":1979200,"uid":320135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"其實佢唱歌真係好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對我嚟講係全港最好，但可惜好死唔死死去奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}